# Strikethrough


## strikethrough

```````````````````````````````` example
~~delete me~~
.
<p><del>delete me</del></p>
````````````````````````````````

```````````````````````````````` example
~~delete me~~~
.
<p><del>delete me</del>~</p>
````````````````````````````````

```````````````````````````````` example
~~delete me\~~~
.
<p><del>delete me~</del></p>
````````````````````````````````

```````````````````````````````` example
~~delete \~\~ me~~
.
<p><del>delete ~~ me</del></p>
````````````````````````````````
